Korektor
========

Korektor is a statistical spell- and (occasional) grammar-checker.

This spellchecker strarted with Michal Richter's diploma thesis
Advanced Czech Spellchecker (https://redmine.ms.mff.cuni.cz/documents/1),
but it is being developed further. There are two versions: a unix command line
utility (tested on Debian, Ubuntu and OS X) and an OS X SpellServer with
a System Service, that integrates with native OS X GUI applications.

Copyright 2014 by Institute of Formal and Applied Linguistics, Faculty of
Mathematics and Physics, Charles University in Prague, Czech Republic.

Korektor website: http://ufal.mff.cuni.cz/korektor
Korektor web service: http://lindat.mff.cuni.cz/services/korektor
Korektor development repository: http://github.com/ufal/korektor
